cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.SY. 

The paper deals with deep neural networks and their performance on computer vision tasks, which suggests that it could belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and systems and control (cs.SY). The focus on predictive uncertainty and safety critical applications further supports these sub-categories. Among these, cs.LG and cs.AI are the most likely sub-categories as they are directly related to the topic of deep neural networks and Bayesian inference.
